This paper deals with compressive sensing measurements and estimation using generalized approximate message passing (GAMP), which are topics related to information theory (cs.IT), signal processing (cs.SP), and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the design of mean-square optimal scalar quantizers, which falls under numerical analysis (cs.NA) and multimedia (cs.MM) categories.
